 and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever supports his own people in their oppression is like a camel that falls dead into a well and is pulled out by its tail.\u201d Source: Musnad Ah\u0323mad 4292 Grade: Hasan (fair) according to Al-Arna'ut \u0639\u0646 \u0639\u0628\u062f\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":3439,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/06\/27\/sabr-tyrants\/","url_meta":{"origin":557,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Tyrants: The Prophet orders patience with unjust rulers","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 27, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Mas\u2019ud reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, after me there will be undue favoritism and matters you will reject.\u201d They said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, what do you order us to do if we reach that time?\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cFulfill\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":775,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2011\/05\/12\/support-oppressed-stop-oppressor\/","url_meta":{"origin":557,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Tribalism: Help the oppressed, stop the oppressor","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 12, 2011","format":false,"excerpt":"Jabir ibn Abdullah reported: Two young men were fighting, one from the Muhajirin and one man from the Ansar. The Muhajir called out, \u201cO Muhajirin!\u201d And the Ansari called out, \u201cO Ansar!\u201d The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, came out and he said, \u201cWhat is this\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/557","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/3712"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=557"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/557\/revisions"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=557"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=557"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=557"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}